EC2fc.yml
_____________
Parameters:
  KeyName:
    Type: AWS::EC2::KeyPair::KeyName
 
Resources:
  MyInstance:
    Type: AWS::EC2::Instance
    Properties:
      AvailabilityZone: us-east-1a
      ImageId: ami-a4c7edb2
      InstanceType: t3.micro
      KeyName: !Ref KeyName

>Next > Specify stack details > Give name > Parameters > KeyName - Select Cloud Form > Next > Next > Submit
> Go to EC2 instances and open using sshkey !! Check SG SSH port 22 enabled or not
